This the the implementation of a management and monitoring system for Digital Signage system.
This is the thesis code implemented at Aalto University.



Introduction to use the application.


Installation:
-------------

Server: Run serverinstaller.sh with sudo

Display: Run displayinstaller.sh with sudo





Configuration:
--------------

Server: Configure ./WebApp/config/database.js and ./Server/ServerConfig.py

Display: Configure ./Client/ClientConfig.py 



Execution
---------

Server: Goto ./Server and sudo node logcollector.js
Client: It should be configured as a Linux service, if required to execute manually, goto ./Client/ and sudo python main.py


External Control: 

Using WebApp
------------ 
It can be executed from  https://<server publicip>:8082
 

Terminal
--------
New Scripts can be created and send to Displays. Few scripts are provided in directory ./Scripts
To Check the output of script run, see directory ./uploadoutput

